Worker: Thank you so much! You saved my life!
Player: I’m just glad I could help, and you’re okay now! Plus, I got some energy from it too, so you really saved me from eternal slumber.
Worker: Glad I could be of assistance then, haha. If I don’t fix this bridge soon, I’m worried I will fall asleep before it’s fixed and then something dangerous could happen…like the truck currently barreling across the bridge!!!
Player: Oh dear, I need to quickly think of something new to draw!